than Betelgeuse or VY Canis Majoris but are

00:03:16.900 --> 00:03:20.440
still 25 to 50 times the diameter of the sun.

00:03:20.440 --> 00:03:24.639
You think about the sun being really huge
to provide all that heat to the earth, but

00:03:24.639 --> 00:03:30.200
